      <title>俄罗斯人正在接受普京在乌克兰的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/putin-starts-new-term-facing-little-opposition-to-russia-s-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统在结束战争的压力不大的情况下开始了新任期，因为民族主义者呼吁集结支持，严厉镇压压制抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/putin-starts-new-term-facing-little-opposition-to-russia-s-war-in-ukraine</guid>
